&lt;h2 id="mermaid"&gt;
 Mermaid
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://mermaidjs.github.io/"&gt;Mermaid&lt;/a&gt; is a library helping you to generate diagram and flowcharts from text, in a similar manner as Markdown.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>